:: Introduction {"position":"325,400","size":"100,100"}
<<set $bg = "videoPanel">>

<span class="top">Hello and welcome to our interview with the creator of the Truman show. How are you doing today?</span>

<span class="bottom-left">[[Good->Question 1]]</span>

<span class="bottom-right">[[Busy, but we'll get through it ->Question 1]]</span>


:: Not Possible {"position":"825,250","size":"100,100"}
High Ratings, High Sponsors, Truman Finds Out


:: Question 1 {"position":"325,525","size":"100,100"}
<span class="top">The Truman Show is a world wide phenomenon, with fans from around the globe. Did you ever expect it to get this big?</span>

<span class="bottom-left">[[Yes, when I came up with the idea of having a main actor who has no idea he is in a show, I knew it would be a huge success. ->Question 2]]</span>

<span class="bottom-right">[[No, I could have never seen this amount of success. ->Question 2]]</span>


:: Question 2 {"position":"325,650","size":"100,100"}
<span class="top">How do you keep this show running 24 hours a day, 365 days a year?</span>

<span class="bottom-left">[[Well, having sponsorships placed around the world help us out a lot and make it so we don't have to run commercials. ->Question 3]]</span>

<span class="bottom-right">[[That's a little industry secret, and a lot of hard work. ->Question 3]]</span>


:: Question 3 {"position":"325,775","size":"100,100"}
<span class="top">Have you ever had any concerns about having a person be trapped in a TV show set, not knowing what the rest of reality is like?</span>

<span class="bottom-left">[[No, of course not. He is living a life most of us would die for. ->Interuption]]</span>

<span class="bottom-right">[[*No Comment* ->Interuption]]</span>


